data.description: Welcome to your dream home located in the heart of Kendall, FL! This great property features 5 bedrooms, two in a half bathrooms, ample space for your family and loved ones. Remodeled kitchen with upgraded appliances with high hats through the kitchen and living area NEW ROOF, Great space with abundance of natural light, providing a warm and welcoming ambiance. Perfectly situated in a quiet and sought after neighborhood, this home is within minutes to grade A schools, shopping malls, major highways, and restaurants. You'll love the convenience of having everything you need right at your fingertips! The spacious bedrooms offer plenty of room for relaxation and tranquility, while the open living areas provide the perfect space for entertaining guests.
